{"id": "1209060606246780948", "channel_id": "1209060606246780948", "type": 0, "author_id": "392840163732226058", "author_name": "vegoutdino", "author_bot": false, "content": "純記錄用，\n原本想逆推一下衰減公式的，\n但技術太差兜不出來，~~還是做成表查表比較快~~\n純紀錄給有興趣的玩家弄弄看，\n某些格子會有兩種數值是因為它數值是有小數點的，\n例如38.4可能對到35、而38.5對到36，就比較難紀錄，\n有想要補充的資料點也可以在下方留言～", "timestamp": "2024-02-19T08:55:11.789000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-02-19T08:56:19.237000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 19}], "attachments": [{"id": "1209060606452432927", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 14266, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1209060606246780948/1209060606452432927/image.png?ex=69cb8bef&is=69ca3a6f&hm=5f4d8e6a118c5e9efbc65e34773172ce1c08661318325ee2402dd5f79f6efb87&"}, {"id": "1209060606695579658", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 5180, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1209060606246780948/1209060606695579658/image.png?ex=69cb8bef&is=69ca3a6f&hm=c3db7a868f913b911c2b0e146aeb0a1cadc4d2549e1d763d6f2ccb483a05e882&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1209060606246780948", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "銀鑰充能與狂氣回充衰減紀錄", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179680056791130"]}
